Package main

Class Market

java.lang.Object
main.Market
public class Market extends Object
This is the Market class. This class controls the logic for buying and selling all purchasable items such as Athletes and Items. It manages the lists of purchasable Athletes and Items, as well as the lists of starter Athletes and weekly purchased Athletes and Items. The Market class is responsible for generating random purchasable Athletes and Items through the GenerateRandom class.
Author:
Yunu Cho, Kush Desai
